WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.480 --> 00:00:02.453
Hey, good morning family.

00:00:02.453 --> 00:00:03.770
Praise the Lord.

00:00:03.770 --> 00:00:05.428
Thank you for joining me.

00:00:05.428 --> 00:00:13.497
It's always such a blessing that every single one of you would want to take your busy day and spend praying with me.

00:00:13.497 --> 00:00:19.119
And Diana is behind the camera today, and she said, "I want you to say hi, babe.

00:00:19.119 --> 00:00:20.560
" "Hi, prayers.

00:00:20.560 --> 00:00:20.983
Hi, prayers.

00:00:21.405 --> 00:00:22.674
" She's behind there.

00:00:22.674 --> 00:00:25.588
I get to look at her now instead of Braden today.

00:00:25.588 --> 00:00:35.760
He's been making shorts for us and getting the Spanish videos out and all the other—he said, "Daddy, I've got to translate all this stuff and get this over on these other channels.

00:00:35.760 --> 00:00:40.080
" So, he's working, and so we're going to make this prayer video for you.

00:00:40.720 --> 00:00:48.480
He is busy trying to translate those videos for South Korea and all the beautiful people all around the world that need to hear the gospel.

00:00:48.480 --> 00:00:49.440
He works so hard.

00:00:49.440 --> 00:00:49.884
He does.

00:00:49.884 --> 00:00:50.996
I'm so proud of him.

00:00:50.996 --> 00:00:51.935
He's a good boy.

00:00:51.935 --> 00:01:09.220
But I got to talk to Sister Billye yesterday, and that was an amazing conversation about the end times because I always run my words around people who judge them to make sure, you know, you don't want to just be spouting off stuff without people really listening to them that have a discerning ear.

00:01:09.220 --> 00:01:17.360
And so I wanted her to really listen to some of the things that the Lord has been sharing with me to see if, you know, you're not getting flaky.

00:01:17.360 --> 00:01:18.320
You don't want to get flaky.

00:01:18.320 --> 00:01:21.085
The Lord told me there's too many voices right now.

00:01:21.085 --> 00:01:25.400
There's too many voices, and there's a lot of them that are listening to familiar spirits.

00:01:25.400 --> 00:01:29.430
And he said, "Brandon, you must test and judge the spirits.

00:01:29.430 --> 00:01:32.819
You must test it so that you don't get off.

00:01:32.819 --> 00:01:39.970
" And that's why I put elders around me, you know, that are seasoned believers that have been in this for a long time.

00:01:39.970 --> 00:01:50.879
But she's been around people—been around Smith Wigglesworth, two different people, and then she's been around, I mean, Lester Sumrall to Kenneth Hagin to all the greats in my opinion, you know.

00:01:51.159 --> 00:02:09.967
Mama Jenkins, Sister Wilkerson, there's Rachel Teafatiller, all the greats, and it's such an honor to even be able to talk to her and that she would call and feel the Holy Spirit would have her call, and I just thank God that I have a mother in the faith that would take time to want to help me.

00:02:10.271 --> 00:02:12.746
I don't take it for granted ever.

00:02:12.746 --> 00:02:16.319
It is truly an honor, and it's humbling.

00:02:16.319 --> 00:02:17.760
And he started talking.

00:02:17.760 --> 00:02:22.800
He said there's a difference between healings and miracles.

00:02:22.800 --> 00:02:29.087
Healing anointing is—and I even talked to Sister Billye about this—she's talking about healings are the children's bread.

00:02:31.130 --> 00:02:33.382
Divine health is the children's bread.

00:02:33.382 --> 00:02:35.800
But miracles are top-notch.

00:02:36.800 --> 00:02:43.840
Seeing creative miracles—arms growing out, legs, eyes coming back, whatever.

00:02:43.840 --> 00:02:46.080
Whenever it's not a healing, it's a miracle.

00:02:46.080 --> 00:02:48.391
It's like a major deal.

00:02:48.391 --> 00:03:03.040
And the Lord said to me, "We're about to start to see people walk in miracles—creative, walking in miracles, healing autistic children, cerebral palsy, Down syndrome, all of it.

00:03:03.040 --> 00:03:09.449
I'm talking about supernatural things that no man will get the glory because there's no man that can do it.

00:03:09.449 --> 00:03:10.731
It's all about Jesus.

00:03:10.731 --> 00:03:14.548
" And I'm telling you all, we're going to see things like we've never seen before.

00:03:14.548 --> 00:03:17.657
But it's going to happen in a 24-hour window.

00:03:17.657 --> 00:03:19.536
The switch will come on.

00:03:19.536 --> 00:03:27.737
And I'm telling you, I talked about this with Sister Billye yesterday about Adam's lease.

00:03:27.737 --> 00:03:30.159
This is a major milestone, something major.

00:03:31.839 --> 00:03:42.240
The switch is going to—and you're going to see creative miracles because what was restrained by what was signed by Adam...

00:03:42.240 --> 00:03:46.311
Even Brother Hagin talked about this, I was told.

00:03:46.311 --> 00:03:55.897
What was brought by the agreement by Adam in the Garden of Eden, when all the things happened with Adam, was a 6,000-year window.

00:03:55.897 --> 00:04:02.619
And I'm telling you all, the 6,000-year window is coming to a close.

00:04:02.619 --> 00:04:07.400
The Lord told me so many times, "Brandon, Adam's lease is up.

00:04:07.400 --> 00:04:14.419
" And within a 24-hour period, you're talking about from night to day.

00:04:14.419 --> 00:04:18.069
That's how much of a change is about to happen in the body of Christ.

00:04:18.069 --> 00:04:25.600
You're about to see stuff you never thought you would see—I mean, you always dreamed you would see, but we've never seen it.

00:04:25.600 --> 00:04:29.600
And the Lord told me, "It's time to get excited.

00:04:29.600 --> 00:04:32.811
I've looked for this moment longer than what you have.

00:04:32.811 --> 00:04:35.440
" And I'm like, "Yeah, Lord, I bet.

00:04:35.440 --> 00:04:36.520
Yeah, of course.

00:04:36.880 --> 00:04:44.960
" He said, "I've longed for this moment more than what you can ever—like your mind can't fathom how long I've waited for this moment.

00:04:44.960 --> 00:04:47.359
" Folks, it's time to get excited.

00:04:47.359 --> 00:04:50.347
And people say, "Well, Brandon, when are you thinking that's going to happen?

00:04:50.347 --> 00:04:51.093
" I don't know.

00:04:51.093 --> 00:04:56.160
He told me to watch the time frame in September all the time.

00:04:56.160 --> 00:05:16.467
Every time we get to the time frame of Rosh Hashanah to Rosh Hashanah, always watch this time frame, for this is a time of a great holy day, a great change, from Rosh Hashanah to Rosh Hashanah.

00:05:16.467 --> 00:05:24.587
This is a time frame of great acceleration, for the birthing pains will triple, double, increase.

00:05:24.587 --> 00:05:31.338
But now is the time of a push.

00:05:31.338 --> 00:05:33.221
We're coming to—it's time to push.

00:05:37.359 --> 00:05:37.559
The baby's coming forth.

00:05:39.759 --> 00:05:47.119
And I have such an anticipation in my spirit for what's about to happen, for the greatest harvest of souls.

00:05:51.020 --> 00:05:52.160
And I'm telling you all, a major volcano is about to go off.

00:06:07.920 --> 00:06:08.507
A major—I want you to hear me again—a major volcano is about to go off.

00:06:25.980 --> 00:06:26.350
And when this goes off, it's going to cause great devastation to the world.

00:06:26.350 --> 00:06:27.691
There's something manipulating our sun.

00:06:27.691 --> 00:06:36.274
There's something manipulating our earth's crust and our Ring of Fire outside of Oregon.

00:06:36.274 --> 00:06:38.400
A major disruption, earthquakes in diverse places.

00:06:38.400 --> 00:06:42.480
But these earthquakes will not just be little tremors anymore.

00:06:57.680 --> 00:06:57.947
I saw major earthquakes that will cause major tsunamis in the days ahead.

00:06:57.947 --> 00:06:59.813
I saw the splitting of Japan.

00:07:09.093 --> 00:07:09.520
I saw major fires in Alaska.

00:07:09.520 --> 00:07:17.460
I saw major gas lines and gas things coming up out of the earth causing major fires in Hawaii, in these areas.

00:07:17.460 --> 00:07:17.871
And the Lord said, "It's not for the believer to fear.

00:07:17.871 --> 00:07:18.000
It's what I told you was coming, for these are the beginning of sorrows.

00:07:18.000 --> 00:07:18.319
" He said, "You must know Psalm 91 and Psalm 23 in the days ahead, for sobering days are coming.

00:07:18.319 --> 00:07:18.343
Very sobering days are coming.

00:07:18.850 --> 00:07:18.1000
" And what's the difference between sober and—I said, "Drunk?

00:07:18.1000 --> 00:07:21.279
" And he said, "Yes, being filled with the Spirit.

00:07:33.871 --> 00:07:34.175
You must remain spiritually hydrated.

00:07:36.1000 --> 00:07:37.360
You must remain spiritually hydrated.

00:07:42.920 --> 00:07:43.140
" I said, "How?

00:07:43.140 --> 00:07:43.700
" By drinking.

00:07:43.700 --> 00:07:49.090
We pour out all the time and we don't drink, and the Lord used this with me.

00:07:57.093 --> 00:07:57.476
He said, "Those that are not hydrated spiritually will become constipated spiritually.

00:07:57.476 --> 00:08:00.239
" That's kind of different, isn't it?

00:08:08.250 --> 00:08:08.639
But those are the things he said.

00:08:08.639 --> 00:08:12.320
"You'll become constipated spiritually if you don't drink enough.

00:08:12.320 --> 00:08:14.834
" How do you become constipated spiritually?

00:08:14.834 --> 00:08:16.960
I'm still praying over that one.

00:08:24.870 --> 00:08:25.180
But the things he said—I guess it's the same thing: if you get really dehydrated in the natural, you get constipated, right?

00:08:25.180 --> 00:08:29.508
I guess because your body does not have enough water.

00:08:29.508 --> 00:08:33.005
But you have to have enough water.

00:08:33.005 --> 00:08:34.148
You must drink.

00:08:36.319 --> 00:08:42.183
"You must drink of my Spirit," he said, "for in the days ahead, very, very sobering things are going to come.

00:08:42.183 --> 00:08:45.680
Great storms are coming, great shakings are coming.

00:08:45.680 --> 00:08:48.903
But how will you survive these shakings?

00:08:48.903 --> 00:08:49.954
By being filled.

00:08:49.954 --> 00:08:52.251
" Be filled with the Holy Spirit.

00:08:52.251 --> 00:08:53.493
Be being filled.

00:08:53.493 --> 00:08:56.091
Be being filled with the Holy Spirit.

00:08:56.091 --> 00:09:04.240
I don't think I've emphasized enough the importance of staying at His feet and drinking—not just of the water.

00:09:04.720 --> 00:09:14.080
This is good water, but drinking of the water of the Word, drinking of His Spirit, worshiping by praying and worshiping Him in these last days.

00:09:14.080 --> 00:09:17.920
That's the only way you're going to make it.

00:09:17.920 --> 00:09:26.320
If you go horizontal and you look at all the stuff that's coming—it's coming when we get to September.

00:09:34.356 --> 00:09:34.551
I need you to hear me.

00:09:36.280 --> 00:09:38.440
When we get to September, by this time next year, you won't even recognize it anymore.

00:09:47.689 --> 00:09:47.991
Just remember I told you this.

00:09:53.680 --> 00:09:54.420
I need you to remember I told you this.

00:09:54.420 --> 00:10:07.680
You will not recognize the earth this time next year because of how much increase we're about to see from this time now, from September.

00:10:07.680 --> 00:10:09.136
We're still in July.

00:10:09.136 --> 00:10:32.240
When we get to August, when we get to September, when we get to these months ahead, we will not recognize where we are this time next year because of how much acceleration of things will take place: from wars and rumors of wars, plagues and pestilences, earthquakes in diverse places, signs in the heavens, but the greatest harvest of souls all at the same time.

00:10:43.736 --> 00:10:44.068
But I want you to get excited at the same time when I'm warning you not to get in fear, because a great harvest of finances is near.

00:10:48.149 --> 00:10:48.419
And it's exciting times.

00:10:48.419 --> 00:10:52.788
He said, "Brandon, this is going to be fun, and the fun has just begun.

00:10:58.267 --> 00:10:58.533
" That is what He told me.

00:10:58.533 --> 00:11:01.120
He said, "The fun has just begun.

00:11:01.120 --> 00:11:04.583
" Brandon, I had this visitation three days ago from the Lord.

00:11:04.583 --> 00:11:07.000
We were eating dinner.

00:11:13.013 --> 00:11:13.226
In the middle of our dinner, we were at the table and He visited.

00:11:18.320 --> 00:11:24.740
The glory came in so strong we lost track of time, and Diana looked at her clock after it was over.

00:11:27.063 --> 00:11:35.900
The visitation was over, and she goes, "Oh my goodness, we've been underneath the glory for over an hour, and our food is cold!

00:11:35.900 --> 00:11:38.424
We had to heat it up in the microwave.

00:11:41.340 --> 00:11:41.800
" It felt like only 15 or 20 minutes.

00:11:41.800 --> 00:11:45.027
Yes, it felt like 15 minutes.

00:11:45.027 --> 00:11:47.360
We got caught up.

00:11:47.360 --> 00:11:49.813
There's no time with the glory.

00:11:49.813 --> 00:11:55.209
You lose track when you're underneath the glory like that; you lose track of time.

00:11:55.209 --> 00:11:59.600
That's why when we get to heaven, there's no time.

00:11:59.600 --> 00:12:16.960
But when you get underneath the glory, it's so strong that it changes you, and you don't even realize how long.

00:12:16.960 --> 00:12:27.200
That's when we went to Sister Billie's camp meeting.

00:12:27.200 --> 00:12:54.160
When we went to her camp meeting, we were there for five hours, and it felt like 20 minutes in that tent.

00:12:54.160 --> 00:13:03.329
And they said, "How long have we been in here?

00:13:03.329 --> 00:13:06.639
" "Five hours.

00:13:06.639 --> 00:13:10.920
" I said, "Are you kidding me?

00:13:10.920 --> 00:13:12.354
Almost over half a day.

00:13:12.354 --> 00:13:14.800
" Seriously, it was a long time, folks.

00:13:15.230 --> 00:13:17.380
And that's what I'm saying.

00:13:17.380 --> 00:13:26.524
When you get underneath the glory, you can be in that for hours, and you just lose track of time because there is no time with the Father.

00:13:26.524 --> 00:13:27.320
It's beautiful.

00:13:33.173 --> 00:13:48.853
I told D, I said when the cloak comes on and I'm seeing over, like I was even today, and then when we had the visitation three days ago, everything—the pressures of life, of finances, the things you go through as a man, as a provider, all the things you go through—you lose track of it.

00:13:50.630 --> 00:13:51.020
And it's beautiful, isn't it?

00:13:51.020 --> 00:13:52.970
Yeah, it seems inconsequential.

00:14:00.107 --> 00:14:00.480
The things that before you felt were such a big deal fade away.

00:14:00.480 --> 00:14:02.011
Yeah, who cares?

00:14:02.011 --> 00:14:07.600
It's like that song: "And the things of this earth grow strangely dim.

00:14:07.600 --> 00:14:14.560
" Yeah, "And the things of this earth will grow strangely dim in the light of His glory and grace.

00:14:14.560 --> 00:14:16.338
" Well, sing it.

00:14:16.338 --> 00:14:26.959
"Turn your eyes upon Jesus, look full in His wonderful face, and the things of earth will grow strangely dim in the light of His glory and grace.

00:14:26.959 --> 00:14:30.819
" Sing it one more time.

00:14:30.819 --> 00:14:39.000
"Turn your eyes upon Jesus, look full in His wonderful face, and the things of earth will grow strangely dim in the light of His glory and grace.

00:14:39.000 --> 00:14:40.300
" Sister Billie saw me.

00:14:40.300 --> 00:15:01.191
She goes, "Brandon, did you know we were talking about the healing ministry and Oral Roberts, and she said Oral Roberts used to walk down the street whenever it first came on his hand, the glory and the fire, and he would go around touching people on the street, and the power of God would heal them.

00:15:08.239 --> 00:15:08.559
" And she said he would go around touching whoever he could on the streets.

00:15:08.559 --> 00:15:10.836
Was it him and Lester Sumrall?

00:15:11.491 --> 00:15:12.473
I believe so, yeah.

00:15:14.933 --> 00:15:19.093
I think she said that Lester Sumrall and him would go around laying hands on people.

00:15:23.400 --> 00:15:23.770
I love hearing those old stories.

00:15:25.960 --> 00:15:35.120
And I go, "Oh, y'all, it's coming again.

00:15:35.120 --> 00:15:35.440
It's coming again.

00:15:37.040 --> 00:15:38.869
The great tent revivals are coming again!

00:15:41.280 --> 00:15:52.400
" And I could see, I was thinking, "Oral Roberts would go around touching people with that glory, and he was running around with Lester Sumrall.

00:15:52.400 --> 00:15:54.560
" I thought, "Get out of here!

00:15:54.560 --> 00:15:56.673
Is that the coolest thing ever?

00:15:56.673 --> 00:16:01.920
" I thought, "Man, goodness, Lord, what an amazing God we serve and what we're about to see.

00:16:01.920 --> 00:16:12.840
" But when you're in that glory and the presence of the Lord is so strong, you lose track of time because there is no time with Him.

00:16:12.840 --> 00:16:14.258
He is time.

00:16:14.258 --> 00:16:17.519
And oh, what an amazing God we serve!

00:16:17.519 --> 00:16:19.199
And He loves us so much.

00:16:19.199 --> 00:16:25.200
He's so patient with every single one of us and all our falls and all our mess-ups.

00:16:25.200 --> 00:16:33.407
He's the ever-present help in a time of need, always there to lift us up and say, "I lift my cup up to You, Father.

00:16:34.751 --> 00:16:35.255
I just need You to fill it up today.

00:16:35.423 --> 00:16:37.973
I need a fresh drink of the living water today.

00:16:41.920 --> 00:16:43.200
" I look forward to the meetings in the fall with Billy Burke this year.

00:16:43.200 --> 00:16:46.171
We're going to travel a lot this fall.

00:16:47.342 --> 00:16:51.199
I told Diana, I said, "I want to go see Billy Burke as much as we can.

00:16:51.626 --> 00:16:56.240
I want to go and be a part of meetings as much as we can in October and in November, anytime we travel.

00:17:14.388 --> 00:17:14.822
" I told Diana, I said, "Let's get us a big minivan or whatever, and let's just go and see what we can see.

00:17:14.822 --> 00:17:18.480
" I think it will be wonderful, don't you?

00:17:18.480 --> 00:17:22.409
I'm just praying that that's what will work out for us.

00:17:22.409 --> 00:17:27.200
But going and getting and dipping in these rivers of glory—I'm so thirsty for it.

00:17:32.970 --> 00:17:33.160
And I'm just anticipating from September of this year things will start to change again.

00:17:43.849 --> 00:17:44.240
The Lord keeps highlighting—He circled the whole month of September.

00:17:56.040 --> 00:17:56.260
He circled it before me, and it was so important to Him to talk about going into October.

00:17:56.260 --> 00:17:57.360
Supernatural windows will open.

00:17:57.360 --> 00:18:03.291
Supernatural doors will open for people that have believed for things that you've been believing and standing and believing for so long.

00:18:07.670 --> 00:18:08.594
And the Lord said, "Brandon, I'm bringing the things of the desires of your heart to pass.

00:18:08.594 --> 00:18:12.640
Get ready for the heart's desires to come to pass at last!

00:18:12.640 --> 00:18:15.200
" Get ready for it, folks.

00:18:15.200 --> 00:18:18.999
It's time to be believing believers, not doubters.

00:18:18.999 --> 00:18:21.910
"Well, I've been believing for so long, brother.

00:18:31.737 --> 00:18:32.091
I don't know if God even cares.

00:18:32.091 --> 00:18:35.160
" You're about to see how much God truly loves you.

00:18:35.160 --> 00:18:36.870
You're about to see it.

00:18:36.870 --> 00:18:38.426
Well, let's go ahead.

00:18:38.426 --> 00:18:40.290
I've talked long enough, D.

00:18:40.290 --> 00:18:42.169
"You've been talking twenty-six minutes.

00:18:42.169 --> 00:18:47.737
" Because I asked her, I said, "Hey, babe, how long have I been talking?

00:18:47.737 --> 00:18:48.423
" "Twenty-six minutes.

00:18:51.618 --> 00:18:53.680
" You see, I told people, "You get on the phone with me, and I keep talking about the glory.

00:18:53.680 --> 00:18:57.360
I'll lose track of time because it's my favorite subject.

00:18:57.360 --> 00:19:05.960
" If you talk to me about things, oh, I talk two or three hours about the glory because it's just my thing, man.

00:19:05.960 --> 00:19:07.280
I love it.

00:19:07.280 --> 00:19:09.379
I get so excited about it.

00:19:09.379 --> 00:19:12.680
They go, "Do you have things to do?

00:19:12.680 --> 00:19:19.400
" I said, "I know, but I'm sure if you do, you'll get off the phone.

00:19:19.400 --> 00:19:21.080
I'm going to bask here.

00:19:21.080 --> 00:19:22.290
" I'm like, "Woo!

00:19:22.290 --> 00:19:22.910
Hallelujah!

00:19:23.840 --> 00:19:24.071
" you know?

00:19:24.071 --> 00:19:27.520
Oh, Father, we thank You, Lord, for what You have for us.

00:19:27.520 --> 00:19:30.808
I'm so thankful, Father, for every single person who's here today.

00:19:30.808 --> 00:19:39.538
And Lord, we want to go tubing.

00:20:11.417 --> 00:20:12.343
But we can't go real tubing without You.

00:20:12.343 --> 00:20:24.679
I'm nothing without Your super on my natural.

00:20:50.480 --> 00:20:51.680
I need it, Father.

00:20:51.680 --> 00:21:33.680
And I thank You, Lord, that if You have anything to say to us today, Father, You'll show us, and You'll show us that which is to come.

00:21:33.680 --> 00:22:02.400
Father, every single person who's coming here, they're hungry for a word, and You speak to them directly in their household right now.

00:22:02.400 --> 00:22:06.594
This is not a Brandon show.

00:22:06.594 --> 00:22:21.172
This is not all about glitz and all that.

00:22:21.172 --> 00:22:38.514
It's all about Jesus and the very spirit of God that dwells on me will dwell on you.

00:22:38.514 --> 00:23:01.580
And I believe with all my heart it's time for every one of us to be believing believers, to hear and see what Jesus has for us to see and what he wants for us.

00:23:01.580 --> 00:23:06.720
Thank you, Father, for the body that was lifted up before us.

00:23:09.333 --> 00:23:10.340
We lift it up before you, Father, in the name of Jesus.

00:23:12.040 --> 00:23:14.089
And we thank you, Lord, that you were bruised for our iniquities.

